{
    "info": {
        "name": "Carpooling - Chat & Notifications API",
        "description": "Chat module (1:1 messaging with booking authorization) and Notification module (in-app + push notifications) for the carpooling backend.",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
    "auth": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "bearer": [
            {
                "key": "token",
                "value": "{{accessToken}}",
                "type": "string"
            }
        ]
    },
    "variable": [
        {
            "key": "baseUrl",
            "value": "http://localhost:3000",
            "type": "string"
        },
        {
            "key": "accessToken",
            "value": "",
            "type": "string"
        },
        {
            "key": "conversationId",
            "value": "",
            "type": "string"
        },
        {
            "key": "receiverId",
            "value": "",
            "type": "string"
        },
        {
            "key": "notificationId",
            "value": "",
            "type": "string"
        },
        {
            "key": "deviceTokenId",
            "value": "",
            "type": "string"
        }
    ],
    "item": [
        {
            "name": "ðŸ“¨ Chat",
            "description": "1:1 chat between rider and driver. Requires a CONFIRMED booking between the two users.",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "List Conversations",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat?limit=20",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "v1",
                                "chat"
                            ],
                            "query": [
                                {
                                    "key": "cursor",
                                    "value": "",
                                    "description": "Cursor for pagination (conversation ID)",
                                    "disabled": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "limit",
                                    "value": "20",
                                    "description": "Number of conversations per page (1-50, default: 20)"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Get paginated list of user's conversations with peer info, last message, and unread count."
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "Get Messages",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/{{conversationId}}/messages?limit=30",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "v1",
                                "chat",
                                "{{conversationId}}",
                                "messages"
                            ],
                            "query": [
                                {
                                    "key": "cursor",
                                    "value": "",
                                    "description": "Cursor for pagination (message ID)",
                                    "disabled": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "limit",
                                    "value": "30",
                                    "description": "Number of messages per page (1-100, default: 30)"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Get paginated messages in a conversation (newest first). User must be a participant."
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "Send Message",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n  \"receiverId\": \"{{receiverId}}\",\n  \"text\": \"Hey! I booked your ride. What's the pickup point?\",\n  \"clientMsgId\": \"msg_client_001\",\n  \"type\": \"TEXT\"\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/send",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "v1",
                                "chat",
                                "send"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Send a message to another user. Requires a CONFIRMED booking between sender and receiver.\n\nFields:\n- `receiverId` (required): UUID of the receiver\n- `text` (required): Message text (1-5000 chars)\n- `clientMsgId` (required): Client-side message ID for idempotency\n- `type` (optional): TEXT (default), IMAGE, FILE, SYSTEM\n- `payloadJson` (optional): Additional structured data\n\n**Error 403**: Chat is only available after a booking is confirmed between rider and driver."
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "Mark Messages as Read",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n  \"lastReadMessageId\": \"message-uuid-here\"\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/{{conversationId}}/read",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "v1",
                                "chat",
                                "{{conversationId}}",
                                "read"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Mark all messages up to `lastReadMessageId` as read in a conversation."
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "Get Unread Count",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/unread-count",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "v1",
                                "chat",
                                "unread-count"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Get total unread message count across all conversations."
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "ðŸ”” Notifications",
            "description": "In-app notifications with Redis-cached unread counts and FCM/APNs push for offline users.",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "List Notifications",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications?limit=20",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "v1",
                                "notifications"
                            ],
                            "query": [
                                {
                                    "key": "cursor",
                                    "value": "",
                                    "description": "Cursor for pagination (notification ID)",
                                    "disabled": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "limit",
                                    "value": "20",
                                    "description": "Number of notifications per page (1-50, default: 20)"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Get paginated list of notifications for the authenticated user (newest first)."
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "Mark Notifications as Read",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n  \"notificationIds\": [\n    \"{{notificationId}}\"\n  ]\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications/read",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "v1",
                                "notifications",
                                "read"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Mark one or more notifications as read.\n\nFields:\n- `notificationIds` (required): Array of notification UUIDs (1-100 items)\n\nInvalidates the Redis unread count cache."
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "Get Unread Count",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications/unread-count",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "v1",
                                "notifications",
                                "unread-count"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Get unread notification count. Uses Redis cache (60s TTL) with DB fallback."
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "Register Device Token",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n  \"platform\": \"android\",\n  \"token\": \"fcm_device_token_from_firebase_sdk\"\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications/devices/register",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "v1",
                                "notifications",
                                "devices",
                                "register"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Register a device token for push notifications (FCM / APNs).\n\nFields:\n- `platform` (required): 'android' or 'ios'\n- `token` (required): Device token from Firebase SDK\n\nUpserts â€” if the token already exists, updates userId and lastSeenAt."
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "Remove Device Token",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "DELETE",
                        "header": [],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications/devices/{{deviceTokenId}}",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "v1",
                                "notifications",
                                "devices",
                                "{{deviceTokenId}}"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Remove a registered device token (e.g. on logout). Only the token owner can delete it."
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "ðŸ”Œ WebSocket Events Reference",
            "description": "These are Socket.IO events, not REST endpoints. Connect via WebSocket with JWT auth token.\n\n**Connection:**\n```\nconst socket = io('http://localhost:3000', {\n  auth: { token: 'your-jwt-token' }\n});\n```\n\n**Chat Events (emit):**\n- `chat:send` â€” Send a message: `{ receiverId, text, clientMsgId, type? }`\n- `chat:typing` â€” Typing indicator: `{ conversationId, receiverId }`\n- `chat:stopTyping` â€” Stop typing: `{ conversationId, receiverId }`\n- `chat:delivered` â€” Delivery receipt: `{ messageId, conversationId }`\n- `chat:read` â€” Read receipt: `{ conversationId, lastReadMessageId }`\n- `chat:sync` â€” Sync missed messages: `{ lastMessageTs }`\n- `presence:ping` â€” Heartbeat\n- `presence:check` â€” Check user status: `{ userId }`\n\n**Chat Events (listen):**\n- `chat:message` â€” New message received\n- `chat:typing` â€” Peer is typing\n- `chat:stopTyping` â€” Peer stopped typing\n- `chat:delivered` â€” Message delivered\n- `chat:read` â€” Messages read\n- `chat:sync` â€” Missed messages batch\n- `presence:status` â€” User online/offline status\n\n**Notification Events (listen):**\n- `notification:new` â€” Real-time notification preview",
            "item": []
        }
    ]
}